      "back_en": "suddenly looking everywhere but at me.",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Fiel."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0xdb5a2",
      "back_en": "The two lock eyes...",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "'travam olhares' aceitável."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0xdb753",
      "back_en": "I asked Nekone to give a periodic report to",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Fragmento coerente."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0xdb781",
      "back_en": "Oshtor, from which she seems to have returned",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Fragmento ok."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0xdb7b4",
      "back_en": "Lord Oshtor summons you. He wishes to make a",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Fiel."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0xdb7e9",
      "back_en": "Oshtor wants a favor?",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Correto."
    },
    {
