      "back_en": "She explicitly used Oshtor's name, not Ukon's...",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Fiel."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0xdb855",
      "back_en": "Oshtor?",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Mantido."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0xdb85d",
      "back_en": "The Oshtor, 'Imperial Guard of the Right'",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "'Like' omitido, ok."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0xdb88b",
      "back_en": "Oshtor? That one of the Twin Shields, Oshtor?",
      "verdict": "revise",
      "note": "'Half of' (um dos dois) perdido."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0xdb8e0",
      "back_en": "I'm Atuy. But hey, you mean that Oshtor,",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Fiel."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0xdb90e",
      "back_en": "right? Oshtor of the Imperial Guard?",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Correto."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0xdb930",
      "back_en": "Are you an acquaintance of his?",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Fiel."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0xdb950",
      "back_en": "Uh, that's...",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Mantido."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0xdb95e",
      "back_en": "Crap, I probably shouldn't talk about this",
      "verdict": "revise",
      "note": "'we' virou singular 'não devia'."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0xdb98c",
      "back_en": "with outsiders around. Our work with him is",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Fiel."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0xdb9ba",
      "back_en": "still secret.",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Correto."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0xdb9c8",
      "back_en": "Acquaintances... Well, not quite.",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Fiel."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0xdb9ec",
      "back_en": "We're his undercover agents.",
      "verdict": "revise",
      "note": "Erro: 'encobertor' (grafia/concordância)."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0xdba66",
      "back_en": "Oh, is that so? Tell me. This Imperial Guard guy.",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Fiel."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0xdbb27",
      "back_en": "I've seen great men, but only a small part",
      "verdict": "revise",
      "note": "'a handful' virou 'pequena parte'."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0xdbbc7",
      "back_en": "reputation.",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Correto."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0xdbc01",
      "back_en": "like him in the world, honestly.",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Fiel."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0xdbd22",
      "back_en": "not introducing you to my dear brother.",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Correto."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0xdbd4a",
      "back_en": "\"Dear brother\"?",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Fiel."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0xdbd5a",
      "back_en": "Uh oh.",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Mantido."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0xdbd69",
      "back_en": "So you're Oshtor's little sister,",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Fiel."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0xdbe22",
      "back_en": "Ah, well. The secret's been revealed anyway.",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Idiom adaptado bem."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0xdbe6e",
      "back_en": "Keep this secret, all right?",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Fiel."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0xdbec2",
      "back_en": "cover our cover in the first place.",
      "verdict": "revise",
      "note": "'cobrir nossa cobertura' redundante/errado."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0xdc0c7",
      "back_en": "Lord Oshtor, I brought them as requested.",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Fiel."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0xdc15d",
      "back_en": "It's so strange. Even though I know it's",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Correto."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0xdc18b",
      "back_en": "Ukon, when he's in Oshtor mode, everything",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Fiel."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0xdc346",
      "back_en": "You can see a little of Ukon in it, honestly--",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Fiel."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0xdc41e",
      "back_en": "Sincere, forthright, no flaw to mention.",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Correto."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0xdc58d",
      "back_en": "So, what did you need to see us about?",
      "verdict": "revise",
      "note": "'ver a gente sobre' é calque tosco."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0xdc6a3",
      "back_en": "Since we're Oshtor's deniable assets,",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Fiel."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0xdc960",
      "back_en": "This must be fate...",
      "verdict": "revise",
      "note": "Erro de grafia 'shér'."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0xdc9a5",
      "back_en": "fateful encounter...",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Correto."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0xdc9ba",
      "back_en": "Did you say something?",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Fiel."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0xdc9cd",
      "back_en": "I accept your request!",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Correto."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0xdc9e8",
      "back_en": "What the hell is she talking about?",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "'blithering' adaptado, ok."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0xdcbc7",
      "back_en": "Ahaha... I can't stop laughing at all this.",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Fiel."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0xdd1b2",
      "back_en": "but to find her among your people...",
      "verdict": "revise",
      "note": "Perde ênfase 'HER of all people'."
    },
